      "path": "audio/narrations/cellular-automata/yunxi/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.32,
      "size": 37152,
      "text": "想象一排格子，每个格子只有黑白两种状态，非死即生。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cellular-automata",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cellular-automata/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.43,
      "size": 38880,
      "text": "时间一步步向前，每个格子的新状态只看它自己和左右两个邻居。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cellular-automata",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cellular-automata/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.63,
      "size": 42048,
      "text": "这就是一维初等元胞自动机，一个规则极简却能生出万千气象的世界。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cellular-automata",
      "section_id": "rule",
      "line_id": "rule-1",
      "filename": "rule-rule-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cellular-automata/yunxi/rule-rule-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.65,
      "size": 42480,
      "text": "一个格子和它的左右邻居，三个格子一共有二的三次方，也就是八种组合。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cellular-automata",
      "section_id": "rule",
      "line_id": "rule-2",
      "filename": "rule-rule-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cellular-automata/yunxi/rule-rule-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.26,
      "size": 36144,
      "text": "我们只要为这八种情形各指定一个输出，就完整定义了一条演化规则。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cellular-automata",
      "section_id": "rule",
      "line_id": "rule-3",
      "filename": "rule-rule-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cellular-automata/yunxi/rule-rule-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.84,
      "size": 45504,
      "text": "八个输出位拼成一个八位二进制数，正好对应零到二百五十五的一个整数，这就是规则号。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cellular-automata",
      "section_id": "chaos",
      "line_id": "chaos-1",
      "filename": "chaos-chaos-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cellular-automata/yunxi/chaos-chaos-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.94,
      "size": 47088,
      "text": "看规则三十，从中间一个黑格出发，长出的图案毫无规律，像纯粹的随机噪声。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cellular-automata",
      "section_id": "chaos",
      "line_id": "chaos-2",
      "filename": "chaos-chaos-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cellular-automata/yunxi/chaos-chaos-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.79,
      "size": 44640,
      "text": "沃尔夫勒姆曾用它的中心列做随机数发生器，简单规则竟能制造出不可预测。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cellular-automata",
      "section_id": "fractal",
      "line_id": "fractal-1",
      "filename": "fractal-fractal-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cellular-automata/yunxi/fractal-fractal-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.85,
      "size": 45648,
      "text": "换成规则九十，新格子等于左右邻居的异或，也就是不同为一、相同为零。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cellular-automata",
      "section_id": "fractal",
      "line_id": "fractal-2",
      "filename": "fractal-fractal-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cellular-automata/yunxi/fractal-fractal-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.75,
      "size": 43920,
      "text": "于是屏幕上浮现出谢尔宾斯基三角，和帕斯卡三角除以二的染色如出一辙。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cellular-automata",
      "section_id": "fractal",
      "line_id": "fractal-3",
      "filename": "fractal-fractal-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cellular-automata/yunxi/fractal-fractal-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "同样的自相似分形，从一条局部规则里自动涌现出来。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cellular-automata",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "inter-1",
      "filename": "interaction-inter-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cellular-automata/yunxi/interaction-inter-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.53,
      "size": 40464,
      "text": "切换到规则一百一十，它已被证明是图灵完备的，能模拟任何计算。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cellular-automata",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "inter-2",
      "filename": "interaction-inter-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cellular-automata/yunxi/interaction-inter-2.mp3",
      "duration": 3.1,
      "size": 49680,
      "text": "亲手换不同的规则号，感受混沌、周期、分形与复杂在同一套系统里此消彼长。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cellular-automata",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cellular-automata/yunxi/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.71,
      "size": 43344,
      "text": "只靠一条局部规则，元胞自动机就走出了混沌、分形与通用计算三条路。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cellular-automata",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cellular-automata/yunxi/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "这提示我们，宇宙的复杂或许并不需要复杂的底层法则。"
    },
    {
